    </div>

    <div class="divide-y hairline border-y hairline">
      <details open class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Berapa lama waktu untuk mencapai band 7?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Tergantung level awal. Dari band 5.5, biasanya 8–12 minggu intensif. Kami beri estimasi pasti setelah tes diagnostik gratis — termasuk skill mana yang harus diperkuat lebih dulu.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Apakah ada jaminan band score?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Kami tidak menjual janji palsu. Tapi &gt;90% siswa kami mencapai target band score mereka di percobaan pertama atau kedua. Kalau belum tercapai, kami beri kelas tambahan gratis — bukan refund yang tidak realistis.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Apakah pengajar native speaker?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Sebagian iya. Kami juga punya pengajar Indonesia bersertifikat CELTA / TESOL — banyak siswa lebih nyaman mulai dengan pengajar lokal lalu pindah ke native saat speaking sudah lancar.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Bagaimana jika saya tidak bisa hadir di kelas?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Setiap kelas direkam — kamu bisa tonton ulang kapan saja di portal siswa. Kami juga jadwalkan kelas pengganti dengan grup level setara.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Bisakah dibantu booking ujian IELTS resmi?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Ya — kami partner dengan British Council dan IDP. Kami bantu pilih center, tanggal, dan jenis ujian (Computer-based atau Paper-based) sesuai timeline kamu.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Apakah ada kelas online?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Iya, kami punya kelas hybrid — kamu bisa pilih offline di centre kami atau live online via Zoom. Banyak siswa kami pakai keduanya bergantian.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Apa beda IELTS Academic dan General Training?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Academic untuk kuliah; General untuk kerja, imigrasi, atau training. Kami bantu memilih yang sesuai dengan tujuan kamu di sesi konsultasi.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group py-5">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-snug pr-6">Apakah pembayaran bisa dicicil?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-9 h-9 rounded-full border hairline flex items-center justify-center text-terra-600 text-xl leading-none">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15.5px] text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[760px]">Iya — kami terima cicilan 0% dengan beberapa bank (BCA, Mandiri, BRI), serta pembayaran QRIS dan virtual account.</p>
